00:02:42,879 --> 00:02:45,447
I don't care if... Who's Joel Pforzheimer?

51
00:02:45,448 --> 00:02:46,914
<i>GQ.</i>

52
00:02:46,915 --> 00:02:49,617
He's been shadowing you
