64
00:03:18,881 --> 00:03:21,749
I understand, but the ad said
the Mac was gonna save the world.

65
00:03:21,750 --> 00:03:23,885
It didn't say it was gonna say hello.

66
00:03:23,886 --> 00:03:25,687
WOMAN #2: We open the house in five.

