00:09:27,884 --> 00:09:32,086
when what I care about is Dan Kottke
sodomizing me in <i>Time</i> magazine.

204
00:09:32,087 --> 00:09:36,390
(sighs) Look. Obviously...

205
00:09:36,391 --> 00:09:38,360
Let me say this to you.

206
00:09:38,361 --> 00:09:41,462
Obviously, Daniel didn't think
he was doing anything wrong.

207
00:09:41,463 --> 00:09:45,033
- By talking to <i>Time</i> about it?
- Yeah.

208
00:09:45,034 --> 00:09:47,067
I don't know what that means.

