because he didn't think
he'd done anything wrong.

215
00:10:03,452 --> 00:10:08,222
Except, Joanna... Except I
don't have a daughter named Lisa.

216
00:10:08,223 --> 00:10:12,159
And this story is now about how I'm
denying paternity and took a blood test.

217
00:10:12,160 --> 00:10:15,496
And that's why there's a picture of...
I don't know what the fuck that is.

218
00:10:15,497 --> 00:10:17,999
That's why there's a
picture of a PC on the cover

219
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:21,570
instead of a picture of me and the Mac.

220
00:10:21,571 --> 00:10:23,938
I don't know what to tell you.

221
00:10:23,939 --> 00:10:27,609
I was supposed to be <i>Time</i>
magazine's Man of the Year.

222
00:10:27,610 --> 00:10:30,279
And then Dan Kottke was born.

223
00:10:35,116 --> 00:10:37,085
- Well...
- What?

224
00:10:37,086 --> 00:10:41,188
- She's waiting for you.
- Who?

225
00:10:41,189 --> 00:10:43,158
- Chrisann.
- Brennan?

226
00:10:43,159 --> 00:10:44,625
