694
00:35:16,997 --> 00:35:20,000
I'm proud of you.

695
00:35:20,001 --> 00:35:23,402
Thank you, boss.

696
00:35:23,403 --> 00:35:27,341
MARKKULA: It's my pleasure to introduce
